By Chibuike Nwabuko Abuja (Sundiata Post) – Unknown gunmen on Wednesday abducted 10 passengers including the driver of an eighteen seater bus along Akure/ Ikere Ekiti. The bus was travelling to Ado-Ekiti from Akure before it was ambushed at one of the bad spots on the route. The heavily armed suspected kidnappers were said to have waylaid a commercial bus along the road and took the passengers to an unknown place. Details Later…